    "description": "This carb smart recipe replaces half the white rice for cauliflower rice. It sizzles, it sears, it has the same smoky aroma \u2013 you won't believe it isn't bacon! You'll also add mushrooms, soy and sesame oil to this plant-based fried rice, and garnish with chilli to serve. Under 600 calories.",
