    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>white long grain rice </strong>and <strong>cauliflower rice</strong> to a pot with a lid with 110ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [175ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[225ml]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once done, remove from the heat and set aside (lid on) to steam until serving</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-meat-free-bacon-fried-cauliflower-rice/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice your<strong> chestnut mushrooms </strong>finely</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-meat-free-bacon-fried-cauliflower-rice/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> meat-free bacon</strong> <strong>lardons</strong> and <strong>sliced mushrooms </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until the meat-free bacon is golden and crispy all over</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-meat-free-bacon-fried-cauliflower-rice/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-meat-free-bacon-fried-cauliflower-rice/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Trim then finely slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> into rounds</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-meat-free-bacon-fried-cauliflower-rice/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free bacon<strong> </strong>has started to crisp, add the <strong>chopped ginger </strong>and <strong>garlic</strong> to the pan and cook for<strong> </strong>1-2 min further or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>cauliflower rice</strong> with your <strong>soy sauce </strong>and<strong> toasted sesame oil </strong>and give everything a good mix up until all the rice is coated</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-meat-free-bacon-fried-cauliflower-rice/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is coated, add your<strong> blanched</strong> <strong>peas</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the<strong> sliced spring onion </strong>(you'll use the rest for garnish!)<strong> </strong>to the pan<strong> </strong>and cook for 2-3 min further \u2013 this is your<strong> smoky meat-free bacon fried cauliflower rice</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-meat-free-bacon-fried-cauliflower-rice/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>smoky meat-free bacon fried cauliflower rice</strong> in a bowl</p><p>Garnish with the<strong> chilli rounds </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>remaining sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
